    "Next, we computed a ten-fold scaffold split for the dataset BBBP (Supplementary Fig. 6).",
    "Scaffold splitting results in a non-uniform distribution of train and test data; this is particularly the case for the first two folds of the ten-fold scaffold split of BBBP (Supplementary Fig. 6).",
